      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POSSIBLE (2) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at Maitland, but was among the placings at this track three back. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Can turn form around here. MR. SPECKLE (7) was out of placings last time (25.72) at Maitland in a Grade 5, finishing seventh and beaten 13 lengths. Has two wins already from this draw. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. SUNBURNT KEEPER (6) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from six tries. Below best last time at Taree Super Track (31.16) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length sixth. Can feature with the right run. MY WEE LASS (5) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
